जय कात्यायनी माता .................

जय कात्यायनी माता .................

अष्ट मात्र का योगिनी , नव नव रूप धरा
जय कात्यायनी माता .................

दोष विकार मिटाके , पावन हमें करो
जय कात्यायनी माता .................

उसने दयामयी माँ , तेरी कृपा पाई
जय कात्यायनी माता .................

हम अति दीन दुखी हैं , कृपा जरा करिये
हैं माँ दोष बहुत पर , आप ना ध्यान धरिये
जय कात्यायनी माता .................

हे कात्यायनी मैया , आरती तेरी गाते
ना धन चाहें ना सोना , प्यार तेरा चाहते
जय कात्यायनी माता .................

snippet.title: Anaganaga Oka Raju - Sankranthi Promo | Naveen Polishetty | Meenakshi | Naga Vamsi S
snippet.description:
The Star Entertainer Naveen Polishetty is back with a hilarious family entertainer this Sankranthi 😎

#AnaganagaOkaRaju is blasting into theatres  - January 14th, 2026 ❤️‍🔥

ఈ సంక్రాంతికి దద్దరిల్లే నవ్వులని ఆనందాన్ని తీసుకొస్తున్నాము….🫶🏻

#AOROnJan14th 💫 

Anaganaga Oka Raju is an upcoming telugu film ft. Naveen Polishetty & Meenakshi Chaudhary in lead roles. Directed by Maari and Produced by Suryadevara Naga Vamsi & Sai Soujanya under Sithara Entertainments and Fortune Four Cinemas. A Mickey J Meyer Musical.

Stars: Naveen Polishetty, Meenakshi Chaudhary
DOP: J Yuvraj
Music: Mickey J Meyer
Directed : Maari
Producer: Naga Vamsi S & Sai Soujanya
Banners: Sithara Entertainments & Fortune Four Cinemas

This world is much deeper than you imagine. Watch the brand-new trailer for Avatar: Fire and Ash and experience it in theatres December 19th.

Also, don’t miss Avatar: The Way of Water back on the big screen in 3D for one week only, starting October 3rd.

With “Avatar: Fire and Ash,” James Cameron takes audiences back to Pandora in an immersive new adventure with Marine turned Na’vi leader Jake Sully (Sam Worthington), Na’vi warrior Neytiri (Zoe Saldaña), and the Sully family. The film, which has a screenplay by James Cameron & Rick Jaffa & Amanda Silver, and a story by James Cameron & Rick Jaffa & Amanda Silver & Josh Friedman & Shane Salerno, also stars Sigourney Weaver, Stephen Lang, Oona Chaplin, Cliff Curtis, Joel David Moore, CCH Pounder, Edie Falco, David Thewlis, Jemaine Clement, Giovanni Ribisi, Britain Dalton, Jamie Flatters, Trinity Jo-Li Bliss, Jack Champion, Brendan Cowell, Bailey Bass, Filip Geljo, Duane Evans, Jr., and Kate Winslet.

snippet.title: India vs Sri Lanka Asia Cup 2025 Super Four Match updates & Analysis
snippet.description:
🎯 LIVE IND vs SL | Asia Cup 2025 Super Four Match 
🔥 Streamed exclusively on 1iQ Gaming — your hub for Asia Cup Super Four action,  Match Insights & Analysis 

📌 Match Details:
🏟️ Venue: Dubai International Cricket Stadium, Dubai 


📅 Date: September 26, 2025 
The Financial Express


🏏 Format: T20 International – Asia Cup Super Four 


🎯 Status: This is a dead rubber match — India have already qualified for the final; Sri Lanka are out of contention. 


👥 Probable Playing XIs:

🇮🇳 India XI: Abhishek Sharma, Shubman Gill, Tilak Varma, Suryakumar Yadav (c), Sanju Samson (wk), Hardik Pandya, Shivam Dube, Axar Patel, Varun Chakaravarthy, Jasprit Bumrah, Kuldeep Yadav 


🇱🇰 Sri Lanka XI: Pathum Nissanka, Kusal Mendis (wk), Kusal Perera, Charith Asalanka (c), Dasun Shanaka, Kamindu Mendis, Wanindu Hasaranga, Chamika Karunaratne, Maheesh Theekshana, Dushmantha Chameera, Nuwan Thushara 


🌤️ Pitch & Weather Outlook:

The Dubai pitch offers pace and bounce, especially early on. Pacers will enjoy trying to exploit any movement. 

As the match progresses, the surface tends to bat better; spin and slower deliveries may find grip in middle overs. 


Forecast: Clear skies, hot conditions (high ~38 °C) with no rainfall expected. 

Toss chances: Chasing may have advantage due to dew under lights. 

📝 Match Context / What to Watch:

India have already secured their spot in the final, so this game can be used to rotate and test bench strength. 

Sri Lanka, eliminated from contention, will try to finish on a high. 


Key battles: India’s top order vs Sri Lankan pace/spin; Sri Lanka’s middle order vs India’s bowlers.

India’s bench & playing XI shuffles will be under scrutiny.

Contiloe Pictures presents Mahayoddha Rama — a next-level 3D animated epic inspired by the timeless Ramayan. Releasing in cinemas nationwide on 17th October 2025, distributed by Cinépolis India.
 
Produced by: Abhimanyu Singh and Roopali Singh (Contiloe Pictures)
